Fight for Control



Aired on 08/03/2012, Narrated by Stephen Bogaert



On 8 June 1983, Reeve Aleutian Airways Flight 8, A Lockheed L-188 Electra, the number 4 propeller separates from the aircraft over Cold Bay, Alaska, causing an explosive decompression and loss of control. The pilots manage to land the aircraft safely at Anchorage, Alaska.
